---------------------------------------------
<div id="em" style="width: 1em; visibility:hidden"></div>
(window.innerWidth / document.getElementById("em").clientWidth) * .625
window.innerWidth / parseFloat(getComputedStyle(document.querySelector('html'))['font-size']) * .625 - getting ems in js
---------------------------------------------

Build process:
    1. Main.sass
    2. Style.comp.css - compilation
    3. Style.concat.css - concatenation
    4. Style.prefix.css - prefixing
    5. Style.css - compressing